CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1955, pg. 27 reads: "Dazzling Displays Exhibit Top Products at Fair...5. the Goode Pharmacy booth lavishly displayed McKesson and Robbins Drug Products. William Goode and petite Miss Gwendolyn Poinsette wear in charge...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: William Goode and Gwen Poinsette posed in Goode Pharmacy booth, in Syria Mosque for the 1955 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
